@startuml
' 备份系统场景顺序图 - BackupEngine 完整备份流水线
' 参与者按交互顺序：用户 -> CLI -> handleBackup -> BackupEngine -> 各管道模块

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFCF6
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

skinparam sequence {
    ActorBorderColor #2C3E50
    ActorFontColor #2C3E50
    ActorBackgroundColor #F39C12
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #2C3E50
    LifeLineBorderColor #2C3E50

    ParticipantBorderColor #2C3E50
    ParticipantFontColor #FFFFFF
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #3498DB
    ParticipantFontSize 13

    BoxBorderColor #BDC3C7
    BoxBackgroundColor #ECF0F1

    ArrowColor #2C3E50
    ArrowFontColor #2C3E50
    ArrowFontSize 11

    NoteBorderColor #BDC3C7
    NoteBackgroundColor #FFF9E6
    NoteFontColor #2C3E50
    NoteFontSize 10

    DividerBackgroundColor #34495E
    DividerFontColor #FFFFFF
    DividerFontSize 12
}

actor       用户          as USER
participant CLI          as CLI
participant "handleBackup\n命令处理器" as HANDLER
participant "BackupEngine\n核心引擎" as ENGINE
participant "FSAbstraction\n文件系统抽象" as FS
participant "CriteriaFilter\n筛选器" as FILTER
participant "Packer\n打包器" as PACK
participant "Compressor\n压缩器" as COMP
participant "Encryptor\n加密器" as ENC
participant "LocalStorage\n存储层" as STORE

== 1. CLI 解析与参数构建 ==

USER -> CLI: **backer backup** <source> <dest>\n[--pack tar] [--compress gzip]\n[--encrypt aes256] [--include-path ...]
activate CLI

CLI -> CLI: CLI11 解析命令行参数
note right: main.cpp: CLI11_PARSE\n→ 填充 BackupOptions 结构体

CLI -> HANDLER: **handleBackup**(source, dest, opts)
activate HANDLER

== 2. 预处理阶段 ==

HANDLER -> HANDLER: create LocalFsAbstraction
note right: commands.cpp:514\nstd::make_unique<LocalFsAbstraction>()
HANDLER -> HANDLER: **buildFilter**(opts)
note right: commands.cpp:87-192\n无条件 → NoopFilter\n有条件 → CriteriaFilter(6维度)
HANDLER -> HANDLER: **buildPacker**(opts.packFormat)
note right: commands.cpp:198-206\n--pack tar → TarPacker\n--pack zip → ZipPacker\n未指定 → nullptr(镜像模式)
HANDLER -> HANDLER: **makeBackupPath**()
note right: 归档模式自动追加后缀\n"backup_20260715.tar"

HANDLER -> ENGINE: **engine.backup**(source, dest, filter, packer)
activate ENGINE

== 3. BackupEngine 内部流水线 ==

ENGINE -> ENGINE: 验证源路径存在且为目录
note right: backup_engine.cpp:32-43\nstd::filesystem::exists\n&& is_directory

ENGINE -> FS: **fs_->walk**(source)
activate FS
FS --> ENGINE: vector<FileEntry>
deactivate FS
note right: backup_engine.cpp:46-54\n递归遍历全部子条目

alt filter != nullptr

    ENGINE -> FILTER: **filter->apply**(entries)
    activate FILTER
    FILTER --> ENGINE: vector<FileEntry>(filtered)
    deactivate FILTER
    note right: criteria_filter.cpp\n路径 / 类型 / 名称 /\nmtime / 大小 / 所有者
else filter == nullptr
    note right: NoopFilter → 直通\nentries 不变
end

alt packer != nullptr  【归档模式】

    ENGINE -> PACK: **packer->pack**(entries, *fs, source, ostream)
    activate PACK
    note right: tar_packer.cpp / zip_packer.cpp\n逐个读取文件 → 打包到内存流
    PACK --> ENGINE: Expected<void, ErrorCode>
    deactivate PACK

    ENGINE -> STORE: **fs_->write**(dest, archiveData, kRegular)
    activate STORE
    note right: 归档二进制写入目标文件
    STORE --> ENGINE: Expected<void, ErrorCode>
    deactivate STORE

else packer == nullptr  【目录镜像模式】

    ENGINE -> FS: **fs_->mkdir**(destination)
    activate FS
    FS --> ENGINE: Expected<void, ErrorCode>
    deactivate FS

    loop 逐条目处理 [遍历 FileEntry 列表]

        ENGINE -> ENGINE: switch(entry.type)
        note right: kRegular / kDirectory /\nkSymlink / kFifo /\nkBlockDevice / kCharDevice

        alt 常规文件
            ENGINE -> FS: **fs_->read**(sourcePath)
            activate FS
            FS --> ENGINE: vector<char>
            deactivate FS

            ENGINE -> STORE: **fs_->write**(destPath, content, kRegular)
            activate STORE
            STORE --> ENGINE: Expected<void, ErrorCode>
            deactivate STORE
        else 目录
            ENGINE -> FS: **fs_->mkdir**(destPath)
            activate FS
            FS --> ENGINE: Expected<void, ErrorCode>
            deactivate FS
        else 符号链接 / FIFO / 设备
            ENGINE -> ENGINE: createSymlink / createFifo / createDevice
        end

        ENGINE -> FS: **fs_->restoreMetadata**(destPath, meta)
        activate FS
        FS --> ENGINE: Expected<void, ErrorCode>
        deactivate FS
    end
    note right: #FFF9E6\n条目处理完毕后:\n最深优先排序 → 批量恢复\n全部延迟目录元数据
end

ENGINE --> HANDLER: BackupResult{success, stats}
deactivate ENGINE

== 4. 后处理阶段（handleBackup 层） ==

opt compressAlgo 非空

    HANDLER -> HANDLER: **buildCompressor**(algo, level)
    note right: commands.cpp:574-589\nGzipCompressor / ZstdCompressor\n/ LzmaCompressor

    HANDLER -> COMP: **transformFile**(archive, compressed, comp, compress)
    activate COMP
    note right: 读取 → 压缩 → 写出\n删除原始未压缩文件
    COMP --> HANDLER: bool success
    deactivate COMP
end

opt encryptAlgo 非空

    HANDLER -> HANDLER: **buildEncryptor**(algo)
    note right: commands.cpp:592-614\nOpenSslEncryptor (AES256/SM4)

    HANDLER -> HANDLER: **resolvePassword**(password)\n[交互式提示]
    note right: 命令行未提供密码时\n终端无回显输入 + 确认

    HANDLER -> ENC: **encryptFile**(archive, encrypted, enc, password)
    activate ENC
    note right: 读取 → 加密 → 写出\n删除原始未加密文件
    ENC --> HANDLER: bool success
    deactivate ENC
end

== 5. 统计输出 ==

HANDLER -> HANDLER: 组装统计信息
note right: totalFiles / totalDirs /\ntotalBytes / skipped / elapsed

HANDLER --> USER: **✓ Backup completed**\n  Archive: ...\n  Files: N   Dirs: M\n  Size: X bytes\n  Skipped: Y\n  Time: Z ms

deactivate HANDLER
@enduml
